---
permalink: /
eleventyComputed:
  title: "{{ site.title }}"
  description: "{{ site.description }}"
---
{% from "macro.njk" import icon as icon %}
<div class="section container-s margin-inline-auto margin-block-end-xxxl">
  <img src="/assets/images/webring-icon.png" alt="Philippine flag">
  <h1 class="fsv-3 text-rose-3">{{ site.title }}</h1>
  <p>{{ site.description }}</p>
  <p class="fs-7">Your blog can be about anything. It can be about design, development, architecture, medicine, cross-stitching, knitting, puzzles, travelling—anything!</p>

  <h2 class="fsv-4 text-rose-3">Members <small class="fsv-7">({{ members | length }} member)</small>
  </h2>
  {% for member in members %}
    {% unfurl member.url %}
  {% endfor %}

  <h2 class="fsv-4 text-rose-3">What's this?</h2>
  <blockquote>
    <p>A community of sites around a common topic, also known as a webring. Each member includes a badge on their site that links to the previous and next sites in the ring. Kids in the 90s used to love it!</p>
    <cite>
      <a href="https://mxb.dev/blog/webring-kit/#h-what%E2%80%99s-a-webring%3F">Max Boeck</a>
    </cite>
  </blockquote>

  <h2 class="fsv-4 text-rose-3">How to join</h2>
  <details class="reveal">
    <summary class="reveal__trigger">If you're a developer…</summary>
    <div class="reveal__body">
      {% include "ui/instructions-dev.njk" %}
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="reveal">
    <summary class="reveal__trigger">If you're <em>not</em> a developer…</summary>
    <div class="reveal__body">
      {% include "ui/instructions-not-dev.njk" %}
    </div>
  </details>

  <h2 class="fsv-4 text-rose-3">Add the banner to your website</h2>
  <p>Once you're in the members list, add this widget anywhere in your site, preferrably somewhere that will be easily seen.</p>
  <div class="fsv-6">{% highlight "html" %}{% include "ui/widget.njk" %}{% endhighlight %}</div>

  <p>It will render this banner that links to the other members:</p>
  {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

  <details class="reveal">
    <summary class="reveal__trigger">Color Schemes (a.k.a Dark and Light Modes)</summary>
    <div class="reveal__body">
      <div class="fsv-6">
    {% set renderStr %}
      The widget supports different color themes and both light and dark color schemes for each theme.

      Add a `scheme` attribute to the `<webring-banner/>` element that is either `light` or `dark` to force a color scheme for the widget. If this attribute is not set, the widget will follow the system color scheme.
    {% endset %}
    {{ renderStr | markdown | safe }}
    {% highlight "html" %}
<p>This banner will follow the system color scheme.</p>
<webring-banner>…</webring-banner>

<p>This banner will always be light mode.</p>
<webring-banner scheme="light">…</webring-banner>

<p>This banner will always be dark mode.</p>
<webring-banner scheme="dark">…</webring-banner>
    {% endhighlight %}

    {% set excludeScript = true %}
    {% set webringClass = 'margin-block-l' %}
    {% set webringScheme = null %}
    <p class="margin-block-start-xxxl">This banner will follow the system color scheme.</p>
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    <p class="margin-block-start-xxxl">This banner will always be light mode.</p>
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    <p class="margin-block-start-xxxl">This banner will always be dark mode.</p>
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
  </div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="reveal">
    <summary class="reveal__trigger">Themes</summary>
    <div class="reveal__body fsv-6">
      {% set renderStr %}
        The `<webring-banner>` also supports multiple themes. Every theme has a light and dark mode. To use a theme, add a `theme` attribute to the `<webring-banner>` element and set it to one of the following values.
      {% endset %}
      {{ renderStr | markdown | safe }}

      {% highlight "html" %}
<webring-banner theme="serif">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="tron">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="coder">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="bading">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="trans">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="plantlike">…</webring-banner>
<webring-banner theme="borderline">…</webring-banner>
    {% endhighlight %}

    {% set excludeScript = true %}
    {% set webringClass = 'margin-block-l' %}
    {% set webringScheme = null %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'serif' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Serif</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'tron' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Tron</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'coder' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Coder</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'bading' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Bading</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'trans' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Trans</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'plantlike' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Plantlike</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}

    {% set webringTheme = 'borderline' %}
    <h4 class="margin-block-start-xxxl fsv-5">Borderline</h4>
    {% set webringScheme = 'light' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    {% set webringScheme = 'dark' %}
    {% include "ui/widget.njk" %}
    </div>
  </details>

  <h2 class="fsv-4 text-rose-3">Create your own webring!</h2>
  <p>If you want to start your own webring, fork <a href="{{ site.repository }}">this project</a> on Github and follow the instructions in the README.</p>

  <a href="{{ site.repository }}" class="primary button">
    {{ icon('github') }}
    Fork on Github
  </a>
</div>